        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>20. April 1830</date>.</p>
            <p>My dear <addressee>Isaac</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">So favorable an opportunity as this, cannot escape<lb/> me to say a
                few words to you. after the lapse of time intervened.<lb/> The state of our
                    <sic>uncle'</sic> health is exceedingly delicate, his limbs will<lb/> scarcely
                bear him along. So debilitated is he by the wretched cough<lb/>
                <sic>attendent</sic> on the asthma. rest has he now by day or night and altho<lb/>
                he has had strength enough to crawl to my office, I really think he<lb/> will
                    <add>not</add> get home without extreme fatigue. I do not mention these
                facts<lb/> with a view of inducing you to come on should it interfere in your<lb/>
                <sic>arrangments</sic>, but I am certain a few days of your company with Uncle<lb/>
                would so gratify him that the experiment is worth trying. Could you<lb/> not be
                spared a few days next week? I am not so sure that I am<lb/> not taking a pain
                myself, a reparability in <add>?</add> remarks that might<lb/> induce you to come on
                at all hazards. Our friend <persName>W. Etting</persName> will take<lb/> you to our
                debilitated &amp; <sic>feable</sic> uncle <add>?</add> and I am only giving<lb/> you
                my own impression what I think would delight him. Contrary to<lb/> any the
                    leach<add>?</add> idea that I had made this communication, hence<lb/>
                <hi rend="underline">should</hi> you come say that your brain that much was sick and
                having</p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p>a few days leisure, you came over to see him.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Mama has been confined to her bed &amp; room for some weeks.<lb/>
                <add>?</add> so far recoverd. I as to speak of coming down <add>שבת</add> God
                willing.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">A letter from <placeName><sic>Cincinnatti</sic></placeName>
                yesterday all well &amp; changes in state gov.<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Happiness attend</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">you.</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <add>?</add>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <persName role="author">W. Judah</persName>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <pb n="2V"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leezer</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(4)">attention</p>
            <p rend="indent(4)"><persName>Mr. <add>?</add> Etting</persName>. <hi rend="indent(2)"
                        ><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></hi></p>
